Package com.here.android.mpa.common

This package includes classes, interfaces, and enumerations that are generally used by other packages in the Android SDK.

See: Description

Package com.here.android.mpa.common Description

This package includes classes, interfaces, and enumerations that are generally used by other packages in the Android SDK.

However, the following classes are key classes that serves as the entry point to services provided by our SDK:

  • MapEngine - is the entry point for all services provided. It must be initialized before using our services.
  • PositioningManager - is the entry point for our positioning service.

For more information, please refer to our User Guide or the documentation provided by the individual classes above.
